*ButtTaskbar:	(20x1, Center, Padding 0 3, Swallow "FvwmScript-Gmail" "Module FvwmScript FvwmScript-Gmail") Action (Mouse 4) 'SendToModule volume SendString 1 1 bump', Action (Mouse 5) 'SendToModule volume SendString 1 2 bump'
